metadata:
  section_id: 7
  section_name: رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا اپنے مبارک بالوں کو خضاب لگانے کا بیان
  hadith_first: 45
  hadith_last: 48

hadiths[4]{hadithnumber,text,grades,reference,international_number,narrator_chain,chapter_intro}:
45,"“I came to the Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) with a son of mine, so he said; ‘Is this your son?’ I said: ‘Yes,\nI acknowledge him!’ He said: ‘He must not harm you, and you must not harm him!’ I also noticed that the grayness of his hair was reddish.”",,,45,"Abu Rimtha informed:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا اپنے مبارک بالوں کو خضاب لگانے کا بیان
46,"“Did Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) dye [his hair]?” He said: “Yes!”",,,46,"Abu Huraira was asked:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا اپنے مبارک بالوں کو خضاب لگانے کا بیان
47,"""I saw Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) come out of his house shaking his head, for he had performed the major ritual ablution, and on his head there was some trace of henna."" (Or he said: saffron. The Shaikh doubted this.)",,,47,"Al-Jahdama, the wife of Bishr ibn al- Khasasiyya, said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا اپنے مبارک بالوں کو خضاب لگانے کا بیان
48,"""I saw the hair of Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace)dyed.”",,,48,"Humaid told us that Anas said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا اپنے مبارک بالوں کو خضاب لگانے کا بیان
